      "pubkey": "dW50cnVzdGVkIGNvbW1lbnQ6IG1pbmlzaWduIHB1YmxpYyBrZXk6IDM5OEVERDk0NkYxQTcwRkUKUldUK2NCcHZsTjJPT2R1dk56bkdKSXZTNGFMWFNNYU1xQ2w0TVRiand0N21rTG9lZGFrVmVsYUUK",
      "endpoints": [
        "https://github.com/runtime-org/runtime/releases/latest/download/latest.json"
      ]
    }
  }
}
